<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>نظام الامتحانات - ICPC ANU Assiut</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style src="indexstile.css">
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-purple-500 font-sans min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="floating absolute top-10 left-10 w-20 h-20 bg-yellow-300 rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
        <div class="floating absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-green-300 rounded-full opacity-50" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
        <div class="spinning absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 w-40 h-40 border-8 border-pink-300 rounded-full opacity-30"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="exam-container" class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-xl p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-md w-full text-center z-10 transform transition duration-500 hover:scale-105">
        <img src="OIP.jpg" alt="ICPC ANU Assiut Logo" class="mx-auto w-24 h-24 mb-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-black">مرحبًا بكم في ICPC ANU Assiut</h1>
        <div id="question-container" class="mb-6">
            <p class="text-black text-lg font-semibold">نظام الامتحانات الإلكتروني</p>
        </div>
        <button onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Login", "Auth")'" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-xl">
            تسجيل الدخول
        </button>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
